lize</a></code> function in the global namespace, which can\nbe used to tag i18n messages in your code that needs to be translated.</p>\n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n  <h2 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"入口點的匯出\">入口點的匯出<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/localize/init#入口點的匯出\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"entry-point-exports\">Entry point exports<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/localize/init#entry-point-exports\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"export-list\">\n    <h3 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"型別\">型別<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/localize/init#型別\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"types\">Types<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/localize/init#types\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <table class=\"is-full-width list-table\">\n      \n      <tbody><tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/localize/init/$localize\">$localize</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p translation-result=\"on\">標記範本文字字串以進行本地化。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Tag a template literal string for localization.</p>\n\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n    </tbody></table>\n  </section>\n  \n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/localize\n - api/localize/init/$localize\n - api/localize/init/LocalizeFn\n - api/localize/init/TranslateFn\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/localize\n - api/localize/init#angularlocalizeinit\n - api/localize/init#entry-point-exports\n - api/localize/init#types\n - api/localize/ini